      "statement": "theorem procedural_associator_cocycle_6b61f251aeab : ((\u2200 {R : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocRing R] (x y z : R\u1d50\u1d52\u1d56),\n      associator x y z = -MulOpposite.op (associator (MulOpposite.unop z) (MulOpposite.unop y) (MulOpposite.unop x))) \u2192\n    (\u2200 {R : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocRing R] (a b c d : R),\n      a * associator b c d - associator (a * b) c d + associator a (b * c) d - associator a b (c * d) +\n          associator a b c * d =\n        0)) \u2227\n  (\u2200 {M : Type _} {S : Set M} {a : M} [Mul M] [HasDistribNeg M] (ha : a \u2208 S.centralizer), -a \u2208 S.centralizer) := by\n  sorry",
